A bold new fee structure was meant to transform the auction
business=E2=80=94lower buyers fees to spur business and end the brutal pric=
e war between the auction houses. But after Sotheby=E2=80=99s struggled to =
land property in all of its main sales centers, it quietly reversed course =
in the final days of the year=E2=80=A6 effectively burying the news.

Marion Maneker ( https://puck.news/author/marion-maneker/?utm_campaign=3DWa=
ll+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_content=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCR=
