&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )
Marion Maneker ( https://puck.news/author/marion-maneker/?utm_campaign=3DWa=
ll+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_content=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCR=
IBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io=
&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )

To hear Sotheby=E2=80=99s tell it, the change in its fee structure
earlier this year was a bold and heroic effort to fix the auction business.=
 And so there was no shortage of defensiveness, last week, when the auction=
 house announced it was walking back those changes, raising the most broadl=
y applicable buyer=E2=80=99s premium from 20 to 27 percent. In an interview=
 ( https://www.theartnewspaper.com/2024/12/19/sothebys-u-turn-on-new-fees-s=
tructure?utm_campaign=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_con=
tent=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_actio=
n&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) with The Art New=
spaper, C.E.O. Charles
Stewart noted defiantly, =E2=80=9CWe are totally unafraid to try things tha=
t challenge conventions in ways that benefit the market and expand access t=
o growing audiences.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0

=C2=A0

But the new fee structure ended up being anything but expansive. Supply in =
the art market was already constrained by other factors=E2=80=94prices have=
n=E2=80=99t gone up in a long time, and collectors just don=E2=80=99t want =
to let things go=E2=80=94and Sotheby=E2=80=99s fee changes, which went into=
 effect after the May sales, made it even harder to land good property to s=
ell. The house had to delay its Hong Kong evening sale of contemporary art =
due to a lack of property; its London day and evening sales were sparse; th=
ere was no day sale in Paris; even in New York, it appeared that Sotheby=E2=
=80=99s finance arm had pushed some lots to the day sale to improve numbers=
=2E But Stewart deflected blame for the=
 failed experiment onto others, compla=
ining that
=E2=80=9Cthe market doubled down on the
status quo=E2=80=9D and pointing a finger at =E2=80=9Cpeople used to consig=
ning with us and those with art advisors.=E2=80=9D

