m_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) back in April, the lower fees looked like par=
t of a Sotheby=E2=80=99s campaign to raise new capital. It=E2=80=99s likely=
 Patrick Drahi and Stewart had to show they were willing to do something dr=
amatic and different in order to get Abu Dhabi=E2=80=99s money. Restructuri=
ng the auction house=E2=80=99s main source of income
certainly qualified, but the audacity to =E2=80=9Cchallenge conventions,=E2=
=80=9D as Stewart put it to The Art Newspaper, isn=E2=80=99t a substitute f=
or execution.=C2=A0

