a brutally competitive marketplace for acquiring property, is a path leadin=
g toward
self-destruction.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0<=
/p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Of course, the auction houses a=
