 lower fees looked like part of a Sotheby=E2=80=99s campaign to raise new c=
apital. It=E2=80=99s likely <strong>Patrick</strong> <strong>Drahi</strong>=
 and Stewart had to show they were willing to do something dramatic and dif=
ferent in order to get Abu Dhabi=E2=80=99s money. Restructuring the auction=
 house=E2=80=99s main source of income
certainly qualified, but the audacity to =E2=80=9C<em>challenge conventions=
</em>,=E2=80=9D as Stewart put it to <em>The Art Newspaper</em>, isn=E2=80=
=99t a substitute for execution.=C2=A0</p></div>
